data.description: IMPROVED PRICE!! Welcome to your MAINTANANCE FREE home located in Shadow Run, Hudson, FL! This beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a standout, situated as an end unit to ensure plenty of natural light fills the space. As you walk in the front door, you will feel right at home! The high ceilings and skylights create an open and airy atmosphere, enhancing the overall sense of space and allowing the natural light to cascade throughout the living areas. The kitchen opens to the living room which is perfect for those that like to entertain family and friends. The spacious master bedroom is located in the back of the home and the master bathroom features a new vanity with a beautiful granite countertop. The screened-in patio of this home provides a tranquil retreat. Whether it's a quiet morning coffee or a relaxing evening with friends, this outdoor oasis becomes an extension of your living space, allowing you to fully embrace the natural beauty that surrounds the home. With a NEW ROOF, NEW APPLIANCES, NO FRONT OR REAR NEIGHBORS, NO Lawn Maintance, and a LOW HOA THAT IS NOT IN A 55+ COMMUNITY, this home won't last. Call today to schedule your showing!
